commit.message:
8355708: Two Float16 IR tests fail after JDK-8345125

Two FP16 tests fail due to IR verification failure in JTREG. Increased the
warmup time to 10000 to make sure it is being compiled by c2 and the
expected IR is being generated.

Testing:
Tested both the testcases with and without these options -
"-ea -esa -XX:CompileThreshold=100 -XX:+UnlockExperimentalVMOptions -server -XX:-TieredCompilation"
and they pass successfully on aarch64.
